title: Guda Audio KickR v1.4-UNION [deepstatus]
description:
Guda Audio KickR v1.4-UNION [deepstatus]

Designed ground up to create nothing but great kicks. Three sections of Body, Thump and Noise For quick but still detailed control. Warm EQ is an old school style EQ that adds very mild saturations when pushing the levers up. Great for sculpting and giving your kicks that extra ohmpf.

Customizeable interface with different color themes and knob styles
CPU friendly
Available for Mac OS X in VST and AU format and for Windows in VST format. Built from ground up in C++.
No brainer price tag

KickR 1.4 - new extended mode on body with pulse modulation and envelope shape knob. added reverb with automatic gate and ducking. thumps support mp3 and ogg
